<L>__{interior fischer's house kitchen}
<A>__{the lights in the kitchen start to flicker. fischer freezes, listening. the house is quiet. fischer dives for the revolver hanging in his holster on the chair. he pulls a container of glowing bullets out of the pocket of his jacket. the container spills on the floor. he scrambles to pick up the bullets and load them into the revolver. fischer edges to the kitchen door, listening, anxious. everything is quiet. he quietly pushes open the door, revolver ready.}
